```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-2.png){width=672}
:::
:::


Notice that the distributions do not have the same shape as the prior. This is particularly true for $\sigma$. 


::: {.cell layout-ncol="2"}

```{.r .cell-code}
